(1130, 100, 1, '∫x cos x dx 应用分部积分,选 u=x,dv=cos x dx,则结果为', '{"A": "x sin x+cos x+C", "B": "x sin x-cos x+C", "C": "x sin x+sin x+C", "D": "-x sin x+C"}', 'A', '分部积分得 x sin x-∫sin x dx=x sin x+cos x+C', 2.00, 3, 100),
